  {
    "type": "hardware-ref",
    "page": "4",
    "id": "hardware-reference",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "HARDWARE — REFERENCE",
        "zh": "五金件 — 参考"
      }
    },
    "entries": [
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ SHCS icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Socket head cap screw (SHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角圆柱头螺钉（SHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Cylindrical head, hex drive. The default fastener for PhysiClaw.ai — used wherever the head can sit above the surface.",
          "zh": "圆柱头，内六角驱动。PhysiClaw.ai 的默认紧固件——只要螺钉头允许凸出表面，都用它。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 4762 / DIN 912",
          "zh": "ISO 4762 / DIN 912"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ BHCS icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Button head cap screw (BHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角盘头螺钉（BHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Domed head, hex drive. Used on surfaces where a lower profile matters but a flush head isn't required.",
          "zh": "圆顶头，内六角驱动。用在需要降低高度、但又无需沉头平齐的表面。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 7380-1",
          "zh": "ISO 7380-1"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ T-nut icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Extrusion T-nut",
          "zh": "型材 T 型螺母"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Drops into a 2020 / 2040 aluminum extrusion channel and locks under a screw head. Every frame-attached part rides on these.",
          "zh": "嵌入 2020 / 2040 铝型材槽，靠螺钉头压紧锁定。所有装到框架上的零件都靠它固定。"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ hex nut icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Hex nut",
          "zh": "六角螺母"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Standard M3 hex nut, paired with a screw to clamp parts together where a T-nut won't fit.",
          "zh": "标准 M3 六角螺母，在 T 型螺母装不下的地方与螺钉配合，把零件夹紧。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 4032 / DIN 934",
          "zh": "ISO 4032 / DIN 934"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ MGN9H icon ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "MGN9H linear rail + slider",
          "zh": "MGN9H 直线导轨 + 滑块"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "9 mm-wide miniature linear guide. Two rails run the Y axis, two more carry the X beam. Mounting pitch is 16 × 15 mm — don't substitute.",
          "zh": "9 mm 宽的微型直线导轨。两条走 Y 轴，另两条承载 X 横梁。安装孔距为 16 × 15 mm——不要用别的替代。"
        }
      },
      {
        "iconLabel": "[ GT2 belt + pulley ]",
        "h3": {
          "en": "GT2 belt &amp; pulley",
          "zh": "GT2 同步带与同步轮"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "2 mm-pitch open-loop belt, clamped at each end of the moving stage. The pulleys are 20-tooth; one per stepper, plus smooth idlers.",
          "zh": "2 mm 齿距的开口同步带，两端分别夹紧在运动平台上。同步轮为 20 齿，每个步进电机配一个，另加光面惰轮。"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "printed-parts",
    "page": "5",
    "id": "printed-parts",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "3D PRINTED PARTS",
        "zh": "3D 打印件"
      }
    },
    "notesBefore": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Part printing settings and guidelines",
          "zh": "零件打印设置与指南"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "PhysiClaw's custom parts are printed by Selective Laser Sintering (SLS), not FDM. A laser fuses nylon powder in a heated powder bed, so parts come out fully solid, support-free, and strong in every direction. This matters here: the parts carry side holes and overhangs that FDM cannot print cleanly. Match the specifications below when sourcing parts.",
          "zh": "PhysiClaw 的定制零件用选择性激光烧结（SLS）打印，而不是 FDM。激光在加热的粉末床里熔结尼龙粉末，打出来的零件完全实心、无需支撑，各个方向都很结实。这一点很关键：这些零件带有侧孔和悬伸，FDM 打不干净。采购零件时请按下面的规格来。"
        },
        "classes": "note"
      }
    ],
    "specs": [
      {
        "k": {
